dct_title_s: San Pablo, Philippine Islands, Laguna Province, Luzon. A.M.S. S901
dct_description_sm: AMS 2. Alternate title: San Pablo. In upper left margin: Philippine city plans 1:5,000 (approx.). Polyconic projection. Relief given by form lines at approximately 20 feet intervals.Compiled from map of San Pablo, Laguna, Philippines, Manila Fire Insurance Association, 1936; Luzon, 1:31,680, Office Dept. Eng., Philippine Dept., No. 35 G, 1912; Vertical Photographs, 1941; oblique photograph, prior to 1940.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1944.
